Altron has signed a rental contract with Growthpoint Properties for a 29,000m² head office in Woodmead. The contract will begin in November 2020 and will bring all nine of Altron’s operating companies under a single roof. The office is currently being used by Deloitte, whose contract will run out at the end of March 2020. Altron’s office will span roughly a quarter of the office park it is in, which offers a lifestyle centre incorporating a gym and creche. “We want our workplace to meet the needs of our employees who don’t only want a modern workplace, but appreciate additional lifestyle services”, said CEO Mteto Nyati. Estienne de Klerk, CEO of Growthpoint South Africa, said: “We are pleased to sign a business of the high calibre of Altron for The Woodlands and look forward to working closely with them”. Renders of the office space can be seen below. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-298150" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-1-608x430.jpg" alt="GRT - Render of Altron 1" width="640" height="452" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-1-608x430.jpg 608w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-1-566x400.jpg 566w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-1-768x543.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-1-1200x848.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-1.jpg 1344w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-298152" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-608x430.jpg" alt="GRT - Render of Altron" width="640" height="452" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-608x430.jpg 608w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-566x400.jpg 566w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-768x543.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron-1200x848.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/GRT-Render-of-Altron.jpg 1344w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />